      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DELIGHTFUL RAIN (1) was unwanted in betting when starting from the same box but ran very well, finishing in the minors over 350m at Traralgon in a Maiden in 20.61. Expected to feature again. MISS IRENE (2) is yet to break through in nine starts but has run a number of placings. Missed the frame when fourth (25.31) at Sale latest but was in the placings the start before. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Should be about the money. HECTIC (4) latest effort finished 3rd in a Bottom Up - Maiden on June 2 over 400m at Warragul behind Aston Espresso beaten 6 lengths (23.38). Looks a key player on best form. WHITE LINE (3) is another with top-three prospects.",
